<doc id="44827" wikidata="Q375616" url="?curid=44827" title="1540s BC">
<text>The 1540s BC was a decade lasting from January 1, 1549 BC to December 31, 1540 BC.
==Events and trends==
* History of ancient Israel and Judah—earliest date for Ahmose I founding the Eighteenth dynasty of Egypt.

==Significant people==
* 1545 BC—Ahmose I, Pharaoh and founder of the 18th Dynasty of Egypt, dies, according to the High Chronology.</text><links>
