<doc id="44859" wikidata="Q2851859" url="?curid=44859" title="1520s BC">
<text>The 1520s BC was a decade lasting from January 1, 1529 BC to December 31, 1520 BC.

==Events==
* 1528 Birth of Dan
* 1525 BC—End of Fifteenth dynasty of Egypt.
* 1522 BC—Jacob migrates to Egypt, settling in the Land of Goshen, according to the Hebrew calendar.
* 1521 BC—April 24—Lunar Saros 36 begins.

==Significant people==

