<doc id="44868" wikidata="Q937712" url="?curid=44868" title="1020s BC">
<text>The 1020s BC is a decade which lasted from 1029 BC to 1020 BC.

==Events and trends==
* 1027 BC — Traditional date for the end of the Shang dynasty in China, and the beginning of the Zhou dynasty.
* 1026 BC — Saul becomes the first king of the Israelites.
* — End of Mycenaean dominance.
* — destruction of Troy.

==Births==
* 1027 BC — Zhao of Zhou

